fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "i18n-module.html#i18ngettext", "fragment": "i18n.gettext \nSets up gettext localisation so that translations are built and placed into their proper locations during install. Takes one positional argument which is the name of the gettext module. \nargs list of extra arguments to pass to xgettext when generating the pot file \ndata_dirs Added list of directories to be set for GETTEXTDATADIRS env var Requires gettext used for local its files \nlanguages list of languages that are to be generated. As of this is optional and the LINGUAS file is read. \npreset Added name of a preset list of arguments current option is glib see source for for their value \ninstall Added if false do not install the built translations. \nThis function also defines targets for maintainers to use Note These output to the source directory \n"});